data.label: About us
data.value:
# Introduction
Guessomania is a Discord app of the popular international game` Alias. We developed with the idea in mind of being user-friendly and easy to use. We always open for new ideas and contributions. If you have any questions or suggestions, feel free to join us in our Discord community server
# Our team
The team behind is passionate team of developers who want to create exciting and fun apps for Discord users
